      <title>金正恩在与俄罗斯交好的同时，对中国给予了温和的赞扬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩以看似克制的言辞向中国国家主席习近平致以问候，而当前平壤正与俄罗斯走得更近，减少对其长期亚洲盟友的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 06:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
